headline: GoDaddy marginally beats quarterly revenue estimates
summary: GoDaddy's incorporation of artificial intelligence has helped attract more businesses to its services as they seek AI tools to grow their digital footprint.  GoDaddy reported second-quarter revenue of $1.22 billion, slightly higher than estimates of $1.21 billion, according to data compiled by LSEG.
